name: CFStreamErrorDomain
desc: Defines constants for values returned in the domain field of the CFStreamError structure.

items.name: case custom
items.desc: The error code is a custom error code.

items.name: case POSIX
items.desc: The error code is an error code defined in errno.h.

items.name: case macOSStatus
items.desc: The error is an OSStatus value defined in MacErrors.h.
